## Recommended Next: Phase 2 (Backend & Persistence)

1. Enable Firebase Auth (`kEnableFirebase = true`)
2. Firestore data persistence for pets, measurements, notes, medications
3. Care circle as Firestore subcollection -- invited users see shared pets
4. Real-time sync across care circle members via Firestore streams
5. Push notifications via FCM
6. Invitation flow: send email, recipient joins via deep link, matched to care circle role

